01:10:24.840 --> 01:10:26.201
ELEANOR: When?

01:10:27.200 --> 01:10:28.731
Tomorrow.

01:10:31.680 --> 01:10:34.042
On the first day of school?

01:10:40.320 --> 01:10:42.090
It's him, isn't it?

01:10:45.520 --> 01:10:48.121
