01:15:16.440 --> 01:15:19.959
<i>ADELE: My doctor said that this
was more common than we thought.</i>

01:15:19.960 --> 01:15:22.686
<i>I was young. We could try again.</i>

01:15:24.320 --> 01:15:26.522
<i>But two more times...</i>

01:15:27.000 --> 01:15:30.204
<i>I'd start feeling the
nausea and the swelling.</i>

01:15:30.800 --> 01:15:32.843
<i>We'd celebrate.</i>

01:15:33.520 --> 01:15:35.722
<i>Began setting up the nursery.</i>

01:15:37.840 --> 01:15:41.203
