01:15:49.520 --> 01:15:51.529
<i>By my fourth time,</i>

01:15:52.520 --> 01:15:54.882
<i>we knew better than to celebrate.</i>

01:15:55.360 --> 01:15:58.159
<i>We knew better than
to tell our friends.</i>

01:15:58.160 --> 01:16:00.519
<i>Or think of baby names.</i>

01:16:00.520 --> 01:16:02.959
<i>We hadn't even packed a
suitcase for the hospital</i>

01:16:02.960 --> 01:16:04.479
<i>when the contractions started.</i>

