01:17:11.200 --> 01:17:14.961
<i>They'd wrapped her in a pink
blanket and put on a diaper.</i>

01:17:16.760 --> 01:17:19.327
<i>The only one she'd ever wear.</i>

01:17:26.280 --> 01:17:30.769
<i>As I stared at this
beautiful little girl,</i>

01:17:32.760 --> 01:17:35.167
<i>her long eyelashes,</i>

01:17:36.440 --> 01:17:40.008
<i>her daddy's nose, my chin,</i>

01:17:43.640 --> 01:17:47.003
<i>the little mouth that would
never take a breath,</i>

01:17:56.480 --> 01:17:59.843
<i>I knew there would be no
further conversations.</i>

01:18:04.480 --> 01:18:06.523
<i>No more attempts.</i>

01:18:09.480 --> 01:18:11.170
<i>We were done.</i>

01:18:32.680 --> 01:18:35.360
<i>The world had become a cruel place.</i>

01:18:38.520 --> 01:18:40.999
<i>I stopped going for walks.</i>

01:18:41.000 --> 01:18:43.679
<i>I couldn't leave the house.</i>

01:18:43.680 --> 01:18:46.119
<i>I couldn't even open
a window at night.</i>

01:18:46.120 --> 01:18:48.527
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

01:18:50.760 --> 01:18:53.406
(SOBBING)

