01:20:04.640 --> 01:20:06.879
<i>everything in the house
had been neatly separated</i>

01:20:06.880 --> 01:20:10.402
<i>into essentials and
things we'd leave behind.</i>

01:20:13.440 --> 01:20:16.759
<i>For no practical reason more than
